HEADWORD: Postboy
<hw>Post"boy`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
rides post horses; a position; a courier.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A boy who carries letters from the post.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Post-captain</ent>⟦br⟧
